issue.title: Make it easier to process bets that aren't numbers
issue.body: For example, "bet five on red" gets recognized as a NumbersIntent; need to train SampleUtterances better

issue.title: Change units to dollars
issue.body: Also localize this to pounds for UK

issue.title: Manage too small bankroll better
issue.body: Users can get stuck if they have a set of bets and the bankroll falls below the last bet amount (e.g. betting 2 units at a time and have 1 unit left).  Perhaps after a spin, if the bankroll is below the last amount bet, we automatically clear those bets and default back to 1 unit per spin?
